sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant FE as Frontend /v2
  participant API as V2 API
  participant RT as CreativeManagerRuntime
  participant ORC as Claude Code Orchestrator
  participant DS as Domain Services
  participant IP as Image Provider
  participant DB as V2 Storage

  U->>FE: Submit prompt or template customization
  FE->>API: POST /api/v2/creative/runs
  API->>DB: Create CreativeRun snapshot
  API->>RT: run deterministic pipeline
  RT->>DS: search_prompt_cases
  DS->>DB: Query active case index
  DB-->>DS: Matching cases
  DS-->>RT: Ranked cases
  RT->>DS: build asset context and template lock
  RT->>ORC: request CreativeOrchestratorDecision via Claude Code model source
  ORC-->>RT: decision or deterministic fallback
  RT->>DS: compose_prompt_plan
  RT->>DS: run_safety_check
  alt safety passed
    RT->>DS: create_image_job
    DS->>IP: Generate image with V2-native provider
    IP-->>DS: Output assets
    DS->>DB: Store outputs, history, provenance, review
    RT->>DB: Save completed CreativeRun
  else blocked or confirmation needed
    RT->>DB: Save blocked/waiting CreativeRun
  end
  API-->>FE: CreativeRun snapshot
  FE-->>U: Show progress and outputs
